The guide and Ennam-Aššur are bringing you seven jugs of wine. There you are to dress the guide in a kusītum from Mama or Talhat.
I paid 8 1/2 shekels of silver for the guard. I paid 2 shekels of silver for the guide who went out before Libur-Bel.
Witness: Peruwa, the guide from Bēt Marila.
4 shekels of silver for the Kanišite guide that I sent.
I paid 1 1/3 mina of tin to the guide of the queen.
I paid the guide of the alahinnum 10 minas of copper to lead me down to the river.
