8 1/2 minas of good copper from Durhimit, up to 14 minas of copper as deduction in Zimishuna, up to 2 minas to Buitak of Tišmurna. 2 minas was the exitšadduātum tax. 15 shekels per donkey I paid to the kaššum-official in Wahšušana. 1 mina per (animal) came on as fees until Purušhaddum.
When my donkeys come down to you from Wulama, you are not to let them remain a single day. Send them straight on to Amriya in Tišmurna
