Make a purchase that will produce at least 10 shekels of silver and send it here. I will do business in Hattuš or Tawiniya.
In regard to the copper belonging to Amur-Ištar, they refused to hand over the copper to my representatives in Purušhaddum, so my journey goes to Purušhaddum
