The Kanešites are bringing you 3 sacks of refined copper weighing 5 talents under my seal. Give them their payment of 6 shekels of silver and instruct my servants to give them something to eat. If you haven't yet brought along my tin, then give it to the Kanešites so that they may bring it together with the sikkum. Pay them five shekels of tin as their wages and let Šamaš-tappa'i go with them
